# Keep HTML (and the Cloudflare control files) LF on every platform. The CSP in
# frontend/public/_headers allow-lists the inline theme script by its SHA-256 hash,
# which is computed over LF bytes — a CRLF checkout on Windows (core.autocrlf=true)
# would change the hash and silently break it on the Linux build. Pinning EOL here
# makes the hash byte-stable across dev and Cloudflare.
*.html      text eol=lf
_headers    text eol=lf
_redirects  text eol=lf
